row.InputSentence1: I was walking in the park one day.
row.InputSentence2: A stranger approached me to ask for change.
row.InputSentence3: I told the man I didn't have any money.
row.InputSentence4: The man kindly said thank you before he walked away.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: Feeling guilty, I bought a restaurant for the stranger.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: Perhaps another person in the park can help him.
